o your digital marketing is simple but powerful. We focus on the essentials: Website Design, SEO, PPC, SMM, &amp; Re-targeting.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:14:\"Graphic Design\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:99:\"Brian knows his way around the Adobe Creative Cloud, and has a team of designers when we need help.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:7:\"Geekery\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:86:\"Joe speaks fluent geek, managing all things technical for the company and our clients.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:87:\"The number of titles per employee is inversely proportional to the number of employees.\";s:23:\"zerif_testimonials_show\";b:1;s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:13:\"Already sold?\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:12:\"Get in touch\";s:29:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:15:\"What about now?\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_title\";s:10:\"Let\'s Talk\";s:24:\"zerif_contactus_subtitle\";s:133:\"Talk isn\'t only cheap, it\'s free. We\'ll discuss your goals and how we may be able to help before we even ask for payment information.\";s:20:\"zerif_googlemap_show\";b:0;s:23:\"zerif_googlemap_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:22:\"zerif_googlemap_static\";b:1;s:22:\"zerif_latest_news_show\";b:0;s:10:\"zerif_logo\";s:86:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/AB-HORZ-Final-Logo_SMALL.png\";s:23:\"zerif_ourfocus_subtitle\";s:33:\"Here are the things that drive us\";s:28:\"zerif_bigtitle_redbutton_url\";s:6:\"#focus\";s:20:\"zerif_ourfocus_title\";s:30:\"<a name=\"focus\"></a> Our Focus\";s:21:\"zerif_socials_twitter\";s:38:\"http://twitter.com/advertisingbrothers\";s:22:\"zerif_socials_linkedin\"